parameters.text:
Analyze this document image and classify it. Provide the following information in JSON format:
{
  "document_type": "one of: Receipt, Invoice, Bill, Statement, Medical_Report, Lab_Results, Prescription, Medical_Invoice",
  "category": "specific category from: Groceries, Electronics, Fuel, Dining, Clothing, Hardware, Pharmacy, Department, Utilities, Transport, Entertainment, Health, Education, Medical, General",
  "vendor": "company or store name if visible",
  "amount": "total amount if visible (include $ symbol)",
  "description": "brief description of the purchase or document",
  "date": "transaction date if visible (DD/MM/YYYY format)",
  "is_medical": "true if this is a medical document (lab results, medical reports, prescriptions, etc.), false otherwise"
}

Classification examples:
- Coles/Woolworths receipt ‚Üí category: "Groceries", is_medical: false
- JB Hi-Fi invoice ‚Üí category: "Electronics", is_medical: false
- Blood test results ‚Üí category: "Medical", document_type: "Lab_Results", is_medical: true
- Doctor's prescription ‚Üí category: "Medical", document_type: "Prescription", is_medical: true
- Medical bill from clinic ‚Üí category: "Health", document_type: "Medical_Invoice", is_medical: true

Analyze this medical document in detail and extract the following information in JSON format:
{
  "patient_name": "full name of the patient if visible",
  "date_of_birth": "patient DOB if visible (DD/MM/YYYY)",
  "test_date": "date of test/examination (DD/MM/YYYY)",
  "doctor_name": "referring or examining doctor name",
  "clinic_name": "medical facility/clinic name",
  "test_type": "type of test (Blood Test, X-Ray, MRI, etc.)",
  "test_results": "key findings or results summary",
  "abnormal_values": "any values outside normal range",
  "recommendations": "doctor recommendations or follow-up",
  "diagnosis": "diagnosis if mentioned",
  "medications": "prescribed medications if any",
  "next_appointment": "follow-up appointment date if mentioned (DD/MM/YYYY)",
  "urgency_level": "Low, Medium, High, Critical based on results",
  "medical_category": "Cardiology, Pathology, Radiology, General, etc."
}

Extract as much medical information as possible from the document. If information is not visible, use 'Not specified'.

‚ùå **Error Processing Document**

An error occurred while processing the document. Please try again or contact support.
